{
  "video_id": "HD4bpztESWw",
  "title": "John Hardy: My green school dream",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17259.0,
      "text": "I grew up"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "in a very small village in Canada,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m an undiagnosed"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "dyslexic."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "I had a really hard time in school."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "In fact, my mother told me eventually"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "that I was the little kid in the village"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 35260.0,
      "text": "who cried all the way to school."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "I ran away."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "I left when I was 25 years old to go to Bali,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 47260.0,
      "text": "and there I met my incredible wife, Cynthia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "and together, over 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "we built an amazing jewelry business."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "It was a fairy tale, and then we retired."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56260.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "Then she took me to see a film"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "that I really didn&#39;t want to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 64259.0,
      "text": "It ruined my life --"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "\"The Inconvenient Truth\" and Mr. Gore."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "I have four kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "and even if part of what he says is true,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re not going to have the life that I had."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "And I decided at that moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "that I would spend the rest of my life"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "doing whatever I could"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 91260.0,
      "text": "to improve their possibilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "and here we are in Bali."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 99260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a tiny, little island --"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 99260.0,
      "end_time": 101260.0,
      "text": "60 miles by 90 miles."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 101260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "It has an intact Hindu culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "Cynthia and I were there."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "We had had a wonderful life there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "and we decided to do something unusual."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "We decided to give back"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "locally."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "And here it is: it&#39;s called the Green School."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "I know it doesn&#39;t look like a school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 125260.0,
      "text": "but it is something we decided to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 125260.0,
      "end_time": 127260.0,
      "text": "and it is extremely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 130259.0,
      "text": "extremely green."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "The classrooms have no walls."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 136260.0,
      "text": "The teacher is writing on a bamboo blackboard."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 136260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "The desks are not square."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 139260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "At Green School, the children are smiling --"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "an unusual thing for school, especially for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "And we practice holism."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "And for me it&#39;s just the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 152260.0,
      "text": "that, if this little girl"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 152260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "graduates as a whole person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "chances are"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 158260.0,
      "text": "she&#39;ll demand a whole world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 158260.0,
      "end_time": 160260.0,
      "text": "a whole world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 160260.0,
      "end_time": 162260.0,
      "text": "to live on."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 162260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "Our children spend 181 days"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "going to school in a box."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "The people that built my school"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "also built the prison and the insane asylum"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "out of the same materials."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 180260.0,
      "text": "So if this gentleman"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 180260.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "had had a holistic education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 182260.0,
      "end_time": 184260.0,
      "text": "would he be sitting there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 184260.0,
      "end_time": 187260.0,
      "text": "Would he have had more possibilities in his life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "The classrooms have natural light."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re beautiful. They&#39;re bamboo."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "The breeze passes through them."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "And when the natural breeze isn&#39;t enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "the kids deploy bubbles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "but not the kind of bubbles you know."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "These bubbles are made from natural cotton"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 208260.0,
      "text": "and rubber from the rubber tree."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "So we basically turned the box"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 210260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "into a bubble."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "And these kids know"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 217260.0,
      "text": "that painless climate control"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 217260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "may not be"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "part of their future."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "We pay the bill at the end of the month,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 226260.0,
      "text": "but the people that are really going to pay the bill"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 226260.0,
      "end_time": 228260.0,
      "text": "are our grandchildren."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "We have to teach the kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 234260.0,
      "text": "that the world is not indestructible."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "These kids did a little graffiti on their desks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 242260.0,
      "text": "and then they signed up for two extra courses."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 245260.0,
      "text": "The first one was called sanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 248260.0,
      "text": "and the second one was called re-waxing."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 251260.0,
      "text": "But since that happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 251260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "they own those desks."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "They know they can control their world."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 261260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re on the grid. We&#39;re not proud of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 261260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "But an amazing alternative energy company in Paris"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "is taking us off the grid with solar."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 269260.0,
      "text": "And this thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 272260.0,
      "text": "is the second vortex to be built in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 272260.0,
      "end_time": 275260.0,
      "text": "in a two-and-a-half meter drop on a river."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 275260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "When the turbine drops in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "it will produce 8,000 watts of electricity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 281260.0,
      "text": "day and night."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 281260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "And you know what these are."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s nowhere to flush."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 285260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "And as long as we&#39;re taking our waste"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 289260.0,
      "text": "and mixing it with a huge amount of water --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 289260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re all really smart, just do the math."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 294260.0,
      "text": "How many people times how much water."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 294260.0,
      "end_time": 296260.0,
      "text": "There isn&#39;t enough water."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 296260.0,
      "end_time": 298260.0,
      "text": "These are compost toilets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "and nobody at the school wanted to know about them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "especially the principal."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 304260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "And they work. People use them. People are okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 310260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s something you should think about doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 314260.0,
      "text": "Not many things didn&#39;t work."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 314260.0,
      "end_time": 317260.0,
      "text": "The beautiful canvas and rubber skylights"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 319260.0,
      "text": "got eaten by the sun in six months."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 319260.0,
      "end_time": 322260.0,
      "text": "We had to replace them with recyclable plastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 326260.0,
      "text": "The teachers dragged giant PVC whiteboards"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 326260.0,
      "end_time": 328260.0,
      "text": "into the classrooms."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 328260.0,
      "end_time": 330260.0,
      "text": "So we had some good ideas:"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 330260.0,
      "end_time": 333260.0,
      "text": "we took old automobile windshields, put paper behind them"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 333260.0,
      "end_time": 335260.0,
      "text": "and created the first alternative"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 335260.0,
      "end_time": 337260.0,
      "text": "to the whiteboard."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 339260.0,
      "end_time": 342260.0,
      "text": "Green School sits in south-central Bali,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 342260.0,
      "end_time": 344260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s on 20 acres"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 344260.0,
      "end_time": 346260.0,
      "text": "of rolling garden."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 346260.0,
      "end_time": 349260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s an amazing river traveling through it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 349260.0,
      "end_time": 351260.0,
      "text": "and you can see there"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 351260.0,
      "end_time": 354260.0,
      "text": "how we manage to get across the river."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 354260.0,
      "end_time": 357260.0,
      "text": "I met a father the other day; he looked a little crazed."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 357260.0,
      "end_time": 359260.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Welcome to Green School.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 362260.0,
      "text": "He said, \"I&#39;ve been on an airplane for 24 hours.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 363260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "I asked him, \"Why?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 369260.0,
      "text": "He said, \"I had a dream once about a green school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 369260.0,
      "end_time": 371260.0,
      "text": "and I saw a picture of this green school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 371260.0,
      "end_time": 373260.0,
      "text": "I got on an airplane."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 373260.0,
      "end_time": 376260.0,
      "text": "In August I&#39;m bringing my sons.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 376260.0,
      "end_time": 378260.0,
      "text": "This was a great thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 378260.0,
      "end_time": 380260.0,
      "text": "But more than that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 380260.0,
      "end_time": 383260.0,
      "text": "people are building green houses around Green School,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 383260.0,
      "end_time": 386260.0,
      "text": "so their kids can walk to school on the paths."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 389260.0,
      "text": "And people are bringing their green industries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 389260.0,
      "end_time": 391260.0,
      "text": "hopefully their green restaurants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 391260.0,
      "end_time": 393260.0,
      "text": "to the Green School."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 393260.0,
      "end_time": 395260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s becoming a community."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 395260.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s becoming a green model."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 398260.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "We had to look at everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 402260.0,
      "text": "No petrochemicals in the pavement."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 402260.0,
      "end_time": 404260.0,
      "text": "No pavement."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 404260.0,
      "end_time": 406260.0,
      "text": "These are volcanic stones laid by hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 406260.0,
      "end_time": 408260.0,
      "text": "There are no sidewalks."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 408260.0,
      "end_time": 411260.0,
      "text": "The sidewalks are gravel. They flood when it rains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 411260.0,
      "end_time": 413260.0,
      "text": "but they&#39;re green."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 413260.0,
      "end_time": 415260.0,
      "text": "This is the school buffalo."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 417260.0,
      "end_time": 420260.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s planning to eat that fence for dinner."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 420260.0,
      "end_time": 422260.0,
      "text": "All the fences at Green School are green."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 422260.0,
      "end_time": 424260.0,
      "text": "And when the kindergarten kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 424260.0,
      "end_time": 426260.0,
      "text": "recently moved their gate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 426260.0,
      "end_time": 429260.0,
      "text": "they found out the fence was made out of tapioca."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 429260.0,
      "end_time": 432260.0,
      "text": "They took the tapioca roots up to the kitchen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 432260.0,
      "end_time": 435260.0,
      "text": "sliced them thinly and made delicious chips."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 435260.0,
      "end_time": 438260.0,
      "text": "Landscaping."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 438260.0,
      "end_time": 440260.0,
      "text": "We manage to keep the garden that was there"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 440260.0,
      "end_time": 443260.0,
      "text": "running right up to the edge of each of the classrooms."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 443260.0,
      "end_time": 445260.0,
      "text": "We dropped them gently in."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 445260.0,
      "end_time": 448260.0,
      "text": "We made space for these guys"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 448260.0,
      "end_time": 451260.0,
      "text": "who are Bali&#39;s last black pigs."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 452260.0,
      "end_time": 454260.0,
      "text": "And the school cow"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 454260.0,
      "end_time": 456260.0,
      "text": "is trying to figure out"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 456260.0,
      "end_time": 458260.0,
      "text": "how to replace the lawnmower"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 458260.0,
      "end_time": 460260.0,
      "text": "on the playing field."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 460260.0,
      "end_time": 462260.0,
      "text": "These young ladies"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 462260.0,
      "end_time": 464260.0,
      "text": "are living in a rice culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 464260.0,
      "end_time": 467260.0,
      "text": "but they know something that few people know in a rice culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 467260.0,
      "end_time": 469260.0,
      "text": "They know how to plant organic rice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 469260.0,
      "end_time": 471260.0,
      "text": "they know how to look after it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 471260.0,
      "end_time": 474260.0,
      "text": "they know how to harvest and they know how to cook it."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 474260.0,
      "end_time": 476260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re part of the rice cycle"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 476260.0,
      "end_time": 478260.0,
      "text": "and these skills will be valuable"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 478260.0,
      "end_time": 480260.0,
      "text": "for them in their future."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 480260.0,
      "end_time": 483260.0,
      "text": "This young man is picking organic vegetables."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 484260.0,
      "end_time": 487260.0,
      "text": "We feed 400 people lunch every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 487260.0,
      "end_time": 490260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s not a normal lunch. There&#39;s no gas."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 490260.0,
      "end_time": 492260.0,
      "text": "Local Balinese women"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 492260.0,
      "end_time": 495260.0,
      "text": "cook the food on sawdust burners"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 495260.0,
      "end_time": 498260.0,
      "text": "using secrets that only their grandmothers know."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 499260.0,
      "end_time": 502260.0,
      "text": "The food is incredible."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 503260.0,
      "end_time": 505260.0,
      "text": "Green School is a place of pioneers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 505260.0,
      "end_time": 507260.0,
      "text": "local and global."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 507260.0,
      "end_time": 509260.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s a kind of microcosm"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 509260.0,
      "end_time": 511260.0,
      "text": "of the globalized world."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 511260.0,
      "end_time": 513260.0,
      "text": "The kids are from 25 countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 513260.0,
      "end_time": 515260.0,
      "text": "When I see them together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 515260.0,
      "end_time": 518260.0,
      "text": "I know that they&#39;re working out"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 518260.0,
      "end_time": 521260.0,
      "text": "how to live in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 521260.0,
      "end_time": 523260.0,
      "text": "Green School is going into its third year"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 523260.0,
      "end_time": 525260.0,
      "text": "with 160 children."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 525260.0,
      "end_time": 527260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a school where you do learn reading --"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 527260.0,
      "end_time": 529260.0,
      "text": "one of my favorites --"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 529260.0,
      "end_time": 531260.0,
      "text": "writing -- I was bad at it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 531260.0,
      "end_time": 533260.0,
      "text": "arithmetic."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 533260.0,
      "end_time": 535260.0,
      "text": "But you also learn other things."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 535260.0,
      "end_time": 537260.0,
      "text": "You learn bamboo building."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 537260.0,
      "end_time": 539260.0,
      "text": "You practice"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 539260.0,
      "end_time": 541260.0,
      "text": "ancient Balinese arts."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 541260.0,
      "end_time": 544260.0,
      "text": "This is called mud wrestling in the rice fields."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 544260.0,
      "end_time": 546260.0,
      "text": "The kids love it."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 546260.0,
      "end_time": 548260.0,
      "text": "The mothers aren&#39;t quite convinced."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 548260.0,
      "end_time": 550260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 550260.0,
      "end_time": 552260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve done a lot of outrageous things in our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 552260.0,
      "end_time": 555260.0,
      "text": "and we said, okay, local, what does \"local\" mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 555260.0,
      "end_time": 557260.0,
      "text": "Local means"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 557260.0,
      "end_time": 559260.0,
      "text": "that 20 percent of the population of the school"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 559260.0,
      "end_time": 561260.0,
      "text": "has to be Balinese,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 561260.0,
      "end_time": 563260.0,
      "text": "and this was a really big commitment."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 563260.0,
      "end_time": 565260.0,
      "text": "And we were right."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 565260.0,
      "end_time": 567260.0,
      "text": "And people are coming forward"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 567260.0,
      "end_time": 570260.0,
      "text": "from all over the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 570260.0,
      "end_time": 573260.0,
      "text": "to support the Balinese Scholarship Fund,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 573260.0,
      "end_time": 577260.0,
      "text": "because these kids will be Bali&#39;s next green leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 577260.0,
      "end_time": 579260.0,
      "text": "The teachers are as diverse"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 579260.0,
      "end_time": 581260.0,
      "text": "as the student body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 581260.0,
      "end_time": 583260.0,
      "text": "and the amazing thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 583260.0,
      "end_time": 585260.0,
      "text": "is that volunteers are popping up."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 585260.0,
      "end_time": 587260.0,
      "text": "A man came from Java"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 587260.0,
      "end_time": 589260.0,
      "text": "with a new kind of organic agriculture."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 589260.0,
      "end_time": 592260.0,
      "text": "A woman came from Africa with music."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 592260.0,
      "end_time": 595260.0,
      "text": "And together these volunteers and the teachers"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 595260.0,
      "end_time": 597260.0,
      "text": "are deeply committed"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 597260.0,
      "end_time": 599260.0,
      "text": "to creating a new generation"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 599260.0,
      "end_time": 602260.0,
      "text": "of global, green leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 603260.0,
      "end_time": 605260.0,
      "text": "The Green School effect --"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 605260.0,
      "end_time": 607260.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t know what it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 607260.0,
      "end_time": 609260.0,
      "text": "We need someone to come and study it."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 609260.0,
      "end_time": 612260.0,
      "text": "But what&#39;s happening, our learning-different kids --"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 612260.0,
      "end_time": 614260.0,
      "text": "dyslexic --"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 614260.0,
      "end_time": 617260.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve renamed them prolexic --"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 617260.0,
      "end_time": 621260.0,
      "text": "are doing well in these beautiful, beautiful classrooms."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 621260.0,
      "end_time": 624260.0,
      "text": "And all the kids are thriving."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 624260.0,
      "end_time": 626260.0,
      "text": "And how did we do all this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 626260.0,
      "end_time": 629260.0,
      "text": "On giant grass."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 629260.0,
      "end_time": 631260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s bamboo."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 631260.0,
      "end_time": 634260.0,
      "text": "It comes out of the ground like a train."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 634260.0,
      "end_time": 637260.0,
      "text": "It grows as high as a coconut tree in two months"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 638260.0,
      "end_time": 640260.0,
      "text": "and three years later it can be harvested"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 640260.0,
      "end_time": 642260.0,
      "text": "to build buildings like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 642260.0,
      "end_time": 646260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s as strong and dense as teak"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 646260.0,
      "end_time": 649260.0,
      "text": "and it will hold up any roof."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 650260.0,
      "end_time": 653260.0,
      "text": "When the architects came, they brought us these things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 653260.0,
      "end_time": 655260.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;ve probably seen things like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 655260.0,
      "end_time": 658260.0,
      "text": "The yellow box was called the administration complex."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 658260.0,
      "end_time": 660260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 660260.0,
      "end_time": 663260.0,
      "text": "We squashed it, we rethought it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 663260.0,
      "end_time": 666260.0,
      "text": "but mainly we renamed it"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 666260.0,
      "end_time": 668260.0,
      "text": "\"the heart of school,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 668260.0,
      "end_time": 670260.0,
      "text": "and that changed everything forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 670260.0,
      "end_time": 672260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a double helix."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 672260.0,
      "end_time": 674260.0,
      "text": "It has administrators in it"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 674260.0,
      "end_time": 676260.0,
      "text": "and many, many other things."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 676260.0,
      "end_time": 678260.0,
      "text": "And the problem of building it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 678260.0,
      "end_time": 680260.0,
      "text": "when the Balinese workers"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 680260.0,
      "end_time": 683260.0,
      "text": "saw long reams of plans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 683260.0,
      "end_time": 686260.0,
      "text": "they looked at them and said, \"What&#39;s this?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 686260.0,
      "end_time": 688260.0,
      "text": "So we built big models."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 688260.0,
      "end_time": 691260.0,
      "text": "We had them engineered by the engineers."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 691260.0,
      "end_time": 693260.0,
      "text": "And Balinese carpenters like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 693260.0,
      "end_time": 696260.0,
      "text": "measured them with their bamboo rulers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 696260.0,
      "end_time": 699260.0,
      "text": "selected the bamboo and built the buildings"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 699260.0,
      "end_time": 702260.0,
      "text": "using age-old techniques,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 702260.0,
      "end_time": 705260.0,
      "text": "mostly by hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 705260.0,
      "end_time": 708260.0,
      "text": "It was chaos."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 708260.0,
      "end_time": 711260.0,
      "text": "And the Balinese carpenters want to be as modern as we do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 711260.0,
      "end_time": 714260.0,
      "text": "so they use metal scaffolding"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 714260.0,
      "end_time": 717260.0,
      "text": "to build the bamboo building"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 717260.0,
      "end_time": 720260.0,
      "text": "and when the scaffolding came down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 722260.0,
      "end_time": 725260.0,
      "text": "we realized that we had a cathedral,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 725260.0,
      "end_time": 727260.0,
      "text": "a cathedral to green,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 727260.0,
      "end_time": 730260.0,
      "text": "and a cathedral to green education."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 730260.0,
      "end_time": 732260.0,
      "text": "The heart of school has seven kilometers"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 732260.0,
      "end_time": 734260.0,
      "text": "of bamboo in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 734260.0,
      "end_time": 736260.0,
      "text": "From the time the foundations were finished,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 736260.0,
      "end_time": 739260.0,
      "text": "in three months it had roofs and floors."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 739260.0,
      "end_time": 742260.0,
      "text": "It may not be the biggest bamboo building in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 742260.0,
      "end_time": 744260.0,
      "text": "but many people believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 744260.0,
      "end_time": 747260.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s the most beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 747260.0,
      "end_time": 750260.0,
      "text": "Is this doable in your community?"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 750260.0,
      "end_time": 752260.0,
      "text": "We believe it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 752260.0,
      "end_time": 755260.0,
      "text": "Green School is a model we built for the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 755260.0,
      "end_time": 758260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a model we built for Bali."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 758260.0,
      "end_time": 761260.0,
      "text": "And you just have to follow these simple, simple rules:"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 761260.0,
      "end_time": 763260.0,
      "text": "be local,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 763260.0,
      "end_time": 765260.0,
      "text": "let the environment lead"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 765260.0,
      "end_time": 767260.0,
      "text": "and think about"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 767260.0,
      "end_time": 771260.0,
      "text": "how your grandchildren might build."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 771260.0,
      "end_time": 774260.0,
      "text": "So, Mr. Gore, thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 774260.0,
      "end_time": 776260.0,
      "text": "You ruined my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 776260.0,
      "end_time": 779260.0,
      "text": "but you gave me an incredible future."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 779260.0,
      "end_time": 781260.0,
      "text": "And if you&#39;re interested in being involved"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 781260.0,
      "end_time": 784260.0,
      "text": "in finishing Green School"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 784260.0,
      "end_time": 786260.0,
      "text": "and building the next 50 around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 786260.0,
      "end_time": 788260.0,
      "text": "please come and see us."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 788260.0,
      "end_time": 790260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 790260.0,
      "end_time": 808260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}